    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/043b7281ac2fed55abecb306f620d914.avif?t=1720597891\" width=616 height=176 /></span><br> “所谓的‘与众不同’，并不是神明的恩赐，而是‘罪过’。<br>——在452b内的疗养员们，全部都是拥有各种各样能力的‘特异能力者’。”<br><br>“多数人不能接受‘特殊的人’与自己的不同，想要将他们‘同类化’，这也是人之常情。<br>——因此，越来越多的疗养员被送往这里。”<br>“然后、金钱换来了痊愈，换来了疗养院的一切，包括我与其他工作人员的工资，等价交换，再公平不过。”<br><br>“只是，唯一一点，一直以来扎根于我心中的疑惑是——<br>……为什么我所照顾的疗养员们从未‘出院’，却没有一位家属提出质疑呢？”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >〇关于角色〇</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/58b718d26be86c08c562aa43843964fa.avif?t=1720597891\" width=200 height=300 /></span><br>卡莉娜<br>疗养院二层与三层的总负责人，维持着疗养院的运行周转。<br>能力：治疗与精神控制<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/e3ec3c300248c7f2794c07d48f2ca6d7.avif?t=1720597891\" width=200 height=300 /></span><br>玛丽<br>新来的疗养员，有些胆怯但很听话的孩子，期望着回家。<br>能力：黑色液体<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/012e455d7d078dc71a2b09d19f9596cd.avif?t=1720597891\" width=200 height=300 /></span><br>诺埃尔<br>随时随地都可以讲出冷笑话的疗养员，友善而随和，热衷于“温暖”。<br>能力：永远寒冷<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/c52c6a0bb8640e956f4b12a69e5b1950.avif?t=1720597891\" width=200 height=300 /></span><br>沃丝<br>乐观而开朗的疗养员，自称是“勇者”，喜欢尝试新奇事物。<br>能力：透视强光下的物体<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/767dec6fa784d7735769f87005624a13.avif?t=1720597891\" width=200 height=300 /></span><br>佐伊<br>沃丝的妹妹，沉稳、冷淡寡言的疗养员，对卡莉娜似乎有些特殊的敌意。<br>能力：透视黑暗中的物体<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/dc1691f7b8d4147481cbba59482b419d.avif?t=1720597891\" width=200 height=300 /></span><br>莫迪<br>可靠的修理工，对各类器械维修得心应手，有着不为人知的过去。<br>能力：无<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/82a55a8374d6253d789d96dc02179601.avif?t=1720597891\" width=200 height=300 /></span><br>奇玛斯•纳塔勒<br>疗养院院长，很关心疗养员们，渴望营造出如同第二个家一样温馨与舒适的疗养院。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/0e9dc5305f4300522c53f2f02eca6bb6.avif?t=1720597891\" width=200 height=300 /></span><br>莱特<br>Beta-T913医护型机器人，疗养院一层与四层的总负责人。<br>作为疗养院的协助管理者提供任何能力所及的服务。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >〇关于游戏〇</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/cc8fbadeb60b831fae163630b331dcc2.poster.avif?t=1720597891\" width=350 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1122750/extras/cc8fbadeb60b831fae163630b331dcc2.webm?t=1720597891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>这是一款横版像素风、剧情向rpg游戏，有部分的探索与解谜要素，<br>也有操作方式简单的qte穿插在游戏流程中。<br><br>[游戏时长]<br>1-2小时<br><br>[结局数量]<br>7<br>当收集齐be3、be4、ne、he后可通过新追加的分支进入te<br><br>[操作方法]<br>方向键进行移动<br>空格/z/Enter 确认/进行调查<br>Esc/x 取消/打开菜单<br>Shift+方向鍵 跑步<br>Alt+Enter 全屏切换",
